+   ```
+7. Check iOS console:
+   ```
+   [Diagnostics] Capturing snapshot for error: ...
+   [Diagnostics] Snapshot sent to Mac
+   ```
+8. Verify diagnostic file created on Mac
+9. Test guard against infinite loop:
+   - Break /diagnose endpoint
+   - Verify diagnostic send fails but doesn't retry infinitely
+
+## Recovery
+If diagnostic capture crashes app:
+- Wrap JSON encoding in try-catch
+- Add nil checks for all optional fields
+- Mark NHR with diagnostic: "DiagnosticSnapshot capture crashed"
+
+## Rollback
+```bash
+cd ~/Projects/sonique-ios
+git revert HEAD
+xcodebuild -project Sonique.xcodeproj -scheme Sonique build
+```
+
+## Notes
+- Mac IP discovery: consider using Bonjour (_sonique._tcp.local)
+- Rate limiting: store last diagnostic send timestamp in memory
+- Don't send diagnostics for cancelled requests (user-initiated)
+- Consider adding diagnostic UI in iOS app settings to view sent diagnostics
